title: Trunk or Treat with Dayton Flyers
text:
Trunk or Treat with Dayton Flyers Where 
6:30 p.m. Thursday, Oct. 29, 2015 Categories 
Events, Kids | Family, On Campus | Alumni Come out to Baujan field at the University of Dayton on Thursday, October 29th as the Women's Soccer team takes on Duquesne at 7:30PM. Prior to the game from 6:30PM to 7:15PM, student organizations will have booths set up inside Collins Gym next to Baujan Field with activities and candy for kids. Admission to the trunk or treat event and the game are FREE. There will also be a costume contest at halftime.
